&lt;p&gt;Due to an internal promotion, we have an exciting opportunity for a Band 6 Occupational Therapist within the Acute Therapy Team at Royal Hampshire County Hospital in Winchester. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will work as part of the in patient service promoting independence with the focus on providing safe and timely discharges from hospital, working across elderly care, medicine, rapid discharge and surgery.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Team are committed to supporting individuals with continued professional development, including regular clinical and managerial supervision, training and team development. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We provide a 7 day service so a commitment to this is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
